{!module: Fmlib_node}

{!module: Fmlib_js}


{2 Main Features}

- Develop console applications once and run them either on nodejs or
  natively ({!module: Fmlib.Io}).

- Develop interactive web applications in the Elm style.

- Combinator parser in the style of [parsec] which fully supports indentation
  sensitivity and incremental parsing. The incrementality guarantees, that the
  parser can run in any environment including a web browser.

- {!module: Fmlib.Pretty_print}: A pretty printer to output nicely formatted
  text and error messages (similar to [Stdlib.Format], but fully monadic to run
  in any environment).

- Library of basic datastructures allowing functional monadic programming
  ({!Fmlib}).
